imdb.plot outline: A drama with a twist of the supernatural, Walking with Angels explores the nature of good and evil and the perceptions we hold of one another. Set in Downtown Los Angeles, we get to know the story of a man who has to confront his demons and face his addiction- an addiction that has changed his life forever. His bond with the other addicts at the recovery group meetings he attends, has been the one thing that has allowed some connection with others dealing with anything like his. We get to know all these people and see their struggles, as events they could never have imagined begin to unfold- events great depths deeper and darker than those dealt with by ordinary people. Unhuman events.
